<div id="node-1188" class="node odd teaser node-type-story">
  
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/archives-submits-residential-school-records-trc" title="Archives submits Residential School records to TRC">Archives submits Residential School records to TRC</a></h2>
  
  <div class="meta">
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>July 2, 2015</p>
<p>After a thorough search of BC Conference Archives for all records related to Indian Residential Schools, Blair Galston finished submitting all historic and present BC Conference residential school records to the Truth and Reconciliation Commission office in Winnipeg this May.</p>
  </div>

    
