<div id="node-1159" class="node even teaser node-type-story">
  
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/content/maverick-jack-comes-conference-archives" title="Maverick Jack comes to Conference Archives">Maverick Jack comes to Conference Archives</a></h2>
  
  <div class="meta">
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p><em><span style="line-height: 19.2000007629395px;">Blair Galston,&nbsp;</span>May 11, 2015</em></p>
<p>Something really special happened at the Archives last month. I received an email from a family that is well-known in these parts&mdash;a family of one of the saints of our church: the Rev. Dr. Jack Shaver (1918&ndash;2001). They were wondering if the Archives would accept a donation of Jack&rsquo;s records. Would we!</p>
  </div>

    
